<L>__{interior apartment night}
<A>__{in the kitchen peter is straightening up. michael joins him, dumping the ashes. peter begins washing the glasses.}
<C>__{peter}
<D>__{where's jack? did he leave?}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{no, he's cuddling up with a blonde named clementine...}
